    "summary": "通过词项到文档的映射实现快速搜索。",
    "tags": [
      "ai"
    ],
    "group": "未分类",
    "draft": false,
    "content": "<h1>Elasticsearch 基础</h1>\n\n<h2>一、核心概念</h2>\n<table>\n  <tr><th>概念</th><th>类比数据库</th></tr>\n  <tr><td>Index</td><td>Database</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Document</td><td>Row</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Field</td><td>Column</td></tr>\n  <tr><td>Mapping</td><td>Schema</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2>二、基本操作</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">PUT /products\nPOST /products/_doc/1 {\"name\": \"iPhone\", \"price\": 999}\nGET /products/_doc/1</code></pre>\n\n<h2>三、常用查询</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-json\">{\n  \"query\": {\n    \"match\": {\"title\": \"苹果\"}\n  }\n}</code></pre>\n\n<h2>四、倒排索引</h2>\n<p>通过词项到文档的映射实现快速搜索。</p>\n"
